    • Field Detail

      • SUBSCR_LIST_PROP_KEY

        public static final String SUBSCR_LIST_PROP_KEY
        Constant SUBSCR_LIST_PROP_KEY is a property key for task instance configuration parameters. With this property you can provide task with initial list of subscribers. These users however must accept subscription first before any message is delivered to them. So you can't force ppl to receive any messages using this setting.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • SUBSCR_LIST_PROP_VAL

        public static final String[] SUBSCR_LIST_PROP_VAL
        Constant SUBSCR_LIST_PROP_KEY is a property value for a key SUBSCR_LIST_PROP_KEY. Please refer to key description for more details. Default value is an empty String array.

      • SUBSCR_RESTRICTIONS_PROP_KEY

        public static final String SUBSCR_RESTRICTIONS_PROP_KEY
        Constant SUBSCR_RESTRICTIONS_PROP_KEY is a property key for task instance configuration parameters. With this property you can decide who can subscribe to the task. Default value is PUBLIC so anybody can subscribe.

      • DESCRIPTION_PROP_KEY

        public static final String DESCRIPTION_PROP_KEY
        Constant DESCRIPTION_PROP_KEY is a description for task instance. Let's say the user want's to create new Interest group for cyclists. This property allows to set some more detailed information about the group like: This is group of ppl interested in mountain cycling near Cambridge.
